### ===== 【完整工作流演示 - 生成所有6种状态的数据】=====
### 用户说明：
### admin(ID=1)
### operator1(ID=2), operator2(ID=3), operator3(ID=4)
### reviewer1(ID=5), reviewer2(ID=6)

### ========== 【第一组：DRAFT 状态 - 草稿】==========

### 1. operator1 创建文章1 - 保持 DRAFT 状态
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Spring Boot 最佳实践",
  "content": "这是一篇关于 Spring Boot 最佳实践的深度文章...",
  "creatorId": 2
}

###

### 2. operator1 创建文章2 - 保持 DRAFT 状态
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Java 并发编程指南",
  "content": "深入理解 Java 并发编程的各种概念...",
  "creatorId": 2
}

###

### ========== 【第二组：PENDING 状态 - 待审核】==========

### 3. operator2 创建文章3
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "数据库性能优化技巧",
  "content": "分享一些常用的数据库性能优化技巧...",
  "creatorId": 3
}

###

### 4. operator2 提交文章3审核 (DRAFT → PENDING)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/3/submit-review?userId=3
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ========== 【第三组：APPROVED 状态 - 审核通过】==========

### 5. operator3 创建文章4
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "微服务架构设计",
  "content": "微服务架构的设计原则和实现方案...",
  "creatorId": 4
}

###

### 6. operator3 提交文章4审核
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/4/submit-review?userId=4
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 7. reviewer1 审核通过文章4 (PENDING → APPROVED)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/audit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": 4,
  "reviewerId": 5,
  "action": "APPROVED",
  "comment": "内容质量不错，审核通过"
}

###

### ========== 【第四组：REJECTED 状态 - 审核拒绝】==========

### 8. operator1 创建文章5
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "API 设计规范",
  "content": "RESTful API 的设计规范和最佳实践...",
  "creatorId": 2
}

###

### 9. operator1 提交文章5审核
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/5/submit-review?userId=2
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 10. reviewer2 审核拒绝文章5 (PENDING → REJECTED)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/audit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": 5,
  "reviewerId": 6,
  "action": "REJECTED",
  "comment": "内容不符合规范，请补充更多技术细节"
}

###

### ========== 【第五组：ONLINE 状态 - 已上线】==========

### 11. operator2 创建文章6
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Git 工作流最佳实践",
  "content": "Git 的分支管理和工作流程规范...",
  "creatorId": 3
}

###

### 12. operator2 提交文章6审核
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/6/submit-review?userId=3
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 13. reviewer1 审核通过文章6
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/audit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": 6,
  "reviewerId": 5,
  "action": "APPROVED",
  "comment": "审核通过，可以发布"
}

###

### 14. operator2 发布文章6上线 (APPROVED → ONLINE)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/6/publish?userId=3
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ========== 【第六组：OFFLINE 状态 - 已下线】==========

### 15. operator3 创建文章7
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Docker 容器化指南",
  "content": "Docker 的基础使用和最佳实践...",
  "creatorId": 4
}

###

### 16. operator3 提交文章7审核
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/7/submit-review?userId=4
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 17. reviewer2 审核通过文章7
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/audit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": 7,
  "reviewerId": 6,
  "action": "APPROVED",
  "comment": "通过审核"
}

###

### 18. operator3 发布文章7上线
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/7/publish?userId=4
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 19. operator3 下线文章7 (ONLINE → OFFLINE)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/7/offline?userId=4
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ========== 【编辑和删除操作】==========

### 20. operator1 编辑文章1（保持 DRAFT 状态）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/content/1?userId=2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Spring Boot 完全指南 - 已更新",
  "content": "更新后的内容：这是一篇更加详细的 Spring Boot 完全指南..."
}

###

### 21. operator1 删除文章2（DELETE DRAFT 状态的内容）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/content/2?userId=2

###

### ========== 【数据查询】==========

### 22. 查看所有内容列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?page=1&pageSize=20

###

### 23. 查看 DRAFT 状态的内容
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?status=DRAFT&page=1&pageSize=10

###

### 24. 查看 PENDING 状态的内容
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?status=PENDING&page=1&pageSize=10

###

### 25. 查看 APPROVED 状态的内容
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?status=APPROVED&page=1&pageSize=10

###

### 26. 查看 REJECTED 状态的内容
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?status=REJECTED&page=1&pageSize=10

###

### 27. 查看 ONLINE 状态的内容
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?status=ONLINE&page=1&pageSize=10

###

### 28. 查看 OFFLINE 状态的内容
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?status=OFFLINE&page=1&pageSize=10

###

### 29. 查看 operator1(ID=2) 创建的内容
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?creatorId=2&page=1&pageSize=10

###

### 30. 查看 operator2(ID=3) 创建的内容
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?creatorId=3&page=1&pageSize=10

###

### 31. 查看 operator3(ID=4) 创建的内容
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?creatorId=4&page=1&pageSize=10

###

### ========== 【操作日志查询】==========

### 32. 查看所有操作日志
GET http://localhost:8080/api/operation-log/list?page=1&pageSize=50

###

### 33. 查看操作日志第2页
GET http://localhost:8080/api/operation-log/list?page=2&pageSize=10

###

